    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically robust, with the critical subframe reinforcement completed and a recent VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains sharp with refreshed bushings and a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the car maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and a clean oil analysis. A visceral, analog performance machine ready for the enthusiast who values mechanical integrity and apex-hunting dynamics.",
