      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard is crack-free. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control and the infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It comes with a comprehensive service log showing regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly, the suspension provides a quiet and composed ride, and the tires have approximately 70% of their tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for its next owner to enjoy without immediate worry or additional investment.",
